                        <interp inst="t18350706-name-402" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS ILSLEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I saw the prisoner that evening at the corner of 8 Shoe-lane, at half past nine o'clock—I saw him at the prosecutor's pocket—he ran past me till he got to the Morning Herald office—he there threw this handkerchief down on the rails—the prosecutor was running after him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
