                        <interp inst="t18350706-name-403" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN HUCKLE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an officer. I saw the prisoner running in advance, and several persons running after him—I ran out of my shop, and threw him down on the steps of the Morning Herald Office—this handkerchief was taken up, and given to me.</p>
